:cypress-spin: *Cypress update for 9/30-10/4*
there were a number of cypress related issues that came up this week:
• :white_check_mark: OAuth issues with creating community user license (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CSY11CK7T/p1727820269744639)
    ◦ fix: during setup, create the oauth token
• :white_check_mark: issue trying to rename project before input is interactable (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CSY11CK7T/p1727901211215419?thread_ts=1727901001.880439&cid=CSY11CK7T)
    ◦ fix: wait until input is loaded before interacting with it
• :white_check_mark: timeout loading build project (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C029ZG026GZ/p1727973911117299?thread_ts=1727972974.534819&cid=C029ZG026GZ)
    ◦ fix: wait until project is interactable (can click upload file button) before continuing with test
• :grey_question: get projects timeout causing flakiness (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C029ZG026GZ/p1728046977072939?thread_ts=1728044813.523069&cid=C029ZG026GZ)
    ◦ temporarily deleted duplicate conversations
• :x: ground truth apps not being deleted causing slow loading and flakiness (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CSY11CK7T/p1728079723972149)
    ◦ pinged BE folks for help in thread
